Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.21,0:00:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次都辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.38,0:00:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡，魏斯洛夫人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.87,0:00:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個月也只有這一點點…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.37,0:00:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人的身體還好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.11,0:00:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次我所乘坐的船艦\N在結束了嚴格的訓練後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.31,0:00:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於得以被編入\N皇帝陛下所屬的艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.85,0:00:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船員們的士氣都十分高昂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.29,0:01:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信在與度西斯的戰役中\N一定可以獲得好的戰果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.39,0:01:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了不負官校首席生之名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.33,0:01:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也為了魏斯洛家的名譽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.23,0:01:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會更勵精圖治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.20,0:01:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好早日成為一名可以帶艦的\N出色的安那托勒軍人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.97,0:01:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好早日成為一名\N出色的安那托勒軍人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.58,0:01:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在為此加緊努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.58,0:01:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過請不要為我擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.58,0:01:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以撐過去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.49,0:01:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我身邊永遠有\N我最好的摯友艾麗絲蒂亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.59,0:01:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我身邊永遠有\N我最好的摯友艾麗絲蒂亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.20,0:01:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…我可以撐過去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.27,0:01:56.64,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,just keep on trying, keep on flying\N{\c&HFFBF00&}just keep on trying, keep on flying
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.71,0:01:59.87,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be the light\N{\c&HFFBF00&}I will be the light
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.31,0:02:07.08,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果說把黎明　當作是一個開始\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜明けをひと　つの始まりとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.46,0:02:14.26,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果說現在就是來臨的時刻\N{\c&HFFBF00&}今が来るべき時だとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.60,0:02:19.29,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,與你的煙雲時代交響曲 飛向雲海的彼端 \N{\c&HFFBF00&}君とのCloud Age Symphony  雲の海の向こうに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.37,0:02:28.67,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,飛往光芒照射的方向\N{\c&HFFBF00&}光が射す方へ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.14,0:02:43.46,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah～是否可以遇見有如魔法的那瞬間？\N{\c&HFFBF00&}Ah～魔法のような一瞬に会えるのか？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.52,0:02:57.96,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,取代寒冷的黑夜  我倆展翅飛翔\N{\c&HFFBF00&}冷たい夜を引き替えに  二人は羽ばたいて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.04,0:03:08.44,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,在那盡頭  抓住了永恆…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}永远を掴む、その果てには
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.26,0:03:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8dccf0&}孤立的小兵\NIsolated pawn
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.13,0:03:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最大航速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.18,0:03:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引擎被…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.41,0:03:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要說話，當心咬到舌頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.92,0:03:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜機中彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.05,0:03:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.39,0:03:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與烏爾班號距離兩百
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.96,0:03:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射多管噴射破甲彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.87,0:04:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掉頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.10,0:04:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掉頭，迴避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.94,0:04:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.94,0:04:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們快離開這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.45,0:04:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去找個安全的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.46,0:04:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.22,0:04:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇，醒醒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.86,0:04:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.23,0:04:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，拉不起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.44,0:04:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾兒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.24,0:04:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.11,0:04:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀之戰艦它…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.71,0:04:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.82,0:04:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烏爾班號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.39,0:04:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要撞上去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.76,0:04:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.58,0:05:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有爆炸聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.48,0:05:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有船身的斷裂聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.02,0:05:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失去銀之戰艦蹤跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.16,0:05:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來我的仕途就到此為止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.69,0:05:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把操縱桿推到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.13,0:05:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接著把左邊的踏板用力踩下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.10,0:05:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.41,0:05:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.11,0:05:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.08,0:06:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉起操縱桿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.65,0:06:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜‧魏斯洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.02,0:07:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是飛鳥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.89,0:07:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神經還真大條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.41,0:08:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左邊的引擎也掛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.00,0:08:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.68,0:08:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起床囉，貪睡鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.49,0:08:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了不負官校首席生之名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.26,0:08:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也為了魏斯洛家的名譽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.20,0:08:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會更勵精圖治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.07,0:09:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好早日成為一名可以帶艦的\N出色的安那托勒軍人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.41,0:09:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.91,0:09:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以撐過去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.31,0:09:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我身邊永遠有\N我最好的摯友艾麗絲蒂亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.43,0:10:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.82,0:10:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快拉節流閥呀，塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.76,0:10:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正也沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.37,0:10:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.90,0:10:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞地亞液不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.64,0:11:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.34,0:11:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次我所乘坐的船艦\N在結束了嚴格的訓練後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.98,0:11:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於得以被編入\N皇帝陛下所屬的艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.45,0:11:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船員們的士氣都十分高昂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.85,0:11:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信在與度西斯的戰役中\N一定可以獲得好的戰果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.92,0:11:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀之戰艦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.56,0:11:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.91,0:11:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星星…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.48,0:11:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星星變得不可靠起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.08,0:12:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾麗絲蒂亞她曾這麼說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.12,0:12:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀之戰艦沈沒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.12,0:12:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都不在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.16,0:12:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們去找銀之戰艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.26,0:12:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信…大家一定都還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.52,0:12:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.24,0:13:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用道謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.38,0:13:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了，快點走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.41,0:13:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要發射了，快退後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.37,0:14:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,輸出功率下降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.58,0:14:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,量體平衡開始瓦解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.34,0:14:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請忍耐一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.04,0:14:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果少了這水\N先鋒艇就飛不起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.93,0:15:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.63,0:15:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.54,0:15:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快幫忙抓住牠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.20,0:15:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以騎著這個…走出沙漠…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.01,0:15:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.32,0:15:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.22,0:15:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鳥呢！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.75,0:15:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.93,0:16:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜\N妳為什麼會坐上銀之戰艦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.04,0:16:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我沒別的地方好待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.14,0:16:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜妳是出身貴族對不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.04,0:16:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.61,0:16:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我看妳對水不是那麼在乎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.31,0:16:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才這麼猜想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.78,0:16:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，我是貴族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.08,0:16:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我們家是那種\N沒辦法遷往新的上層土地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.02,0:16:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能留在舊市區的沒落貴族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.96,0:16:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我在官校還曾經拼到榜首
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.96,0:16:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別看我這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.83,0:16:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我當時可是個\N拿獎學金的資優生呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.03,0:16:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳真厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.30,0:16:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自以為是資優生\N被捧一下就不知天高地厚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.48,0:16:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來我是太小看軍隊的訓練了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.49,0:17:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許沒落貴族無論到哪兒去\N都只有沒落一途吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.96,0:17:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.46,0:17:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我父親和拉薇的父親\N都是先鋒艇駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.90,0:17:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.00,0:17:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但就在他們要送和平書簡\N到度西斯的時候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.11,0:17:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說的是漢密克‧沃卡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.84,0:17:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道我父親嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.98,0:17:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漢密克‧沃卡和喬治‧海德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.05,0:17:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要是先鋒艇駕駛員\N沒有人不知道他們的大名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.62,0:17:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望有一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.49,0:17:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也能和拉薇一起到那裡闖闖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.69,0:17:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大風暴區是一個\N拒絕所有東西進入的怪獸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.50,0:17:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至連銀之戰艦\N在那裡都曾受過很大的損傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.37,0:17:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換了先鋒艇的話\N連三分鐘都撐不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.84,0:17:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在有如怪物一般的狂風裡\N機身不斷發出悲鳴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.11,0:18:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我因為不想認輸\N所以緊緊抓著操縱桿不放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.41,0:18:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是機身彷彿就像要解體似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.61,0:18:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外板一片接一片的被吹走…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.02,0:18:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.45,0:18:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過去我只有從先鋒艇\N參賽者之間聽過這個傳聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.56,0:18:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不就是從一些吹牛故事裡\N聽過大風暴區的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.09,0:18:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我這還是頭一次聽到\N實際去過那裡的人的經驗談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.83,0:18:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他們實在是太厲害了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.10,0:18:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是很厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.81,0:18:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要作繞流處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.28,0:18:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞地亞液的循環距離\N可能不太夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.38,0:18:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過只要儘量多繞幾圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.42,0:18:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該還是可以浮起\N一個人的高度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.82,0:18:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情況如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.06,0:18:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,750…1000…1500
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.73,0:18:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要能到達2500轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.40,0:18:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並能夠維持馬力\N不至於突然下降
